  "title": "Assistant Electrical Engineer",
  "description": "<ul><li>Supervise/perform fault diagnosis, troubleshooting and maintenance of power system/component in workshops and onboard vessels.<br /></li><li>Liaise with various departments within company and client to expedite the scope of work.<br /></li><li>Lead a team of electricians in corrective and preventive maintenance.<br /></li><li>Prepare work completion reports for Customer’s Acceptance.<br /></li><li>Perform maintenance works in accordance with vessel safety requirement.<br /></li><li>Conduct in-depth troubleshooting of electrical connections and Programmable Logic Controllers (PLC) programs.<br /></li><li>Coordinate with vendors and partners, conduct design reviews with customers, and maintain documentation according to our ISO quality systems.<br /></li></ul>",
